videos.description: Jake Lindsey steals and dishes it out to King McClure who finds an open lane for a layup.
videos.headline: Baylor's Lindsey finds McClure for layup

videos.description: Kerwin Roach III lobs it up to Mohamed Bamba who slams it down for a two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Texas' Bamba punishes the rim

videos.description: Mohamed Bamba uses all of his 6-foot-11 height to block Baylor's 7-foot Jo Lual-Acuil Jr.'s shot.
videos.headline: Texas' Bamba blocks shot

videos.description: Terry Maston uses his defensive skills to fake out Texas' Mohamed Bamba to create space and bank in a layup.
videos.headline: Baylor's Maston fakes out Bamba for layup

videos.description: Manu Lecomte just beats the shot clock to drill a clutch jumper in OT against Texas.
videos.headline: Baylor's Lecomte drains clutch jumper

videos.description: Manu Lecomte misses his shot but Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. capitalizes on the miss with a putback dunk to go ahead of Texas in the final seconds of double overtime.
videos.headline: Baylor's Lual-Acuil Jr. delivers dagger putback dunk

videos.description: With both teams heading into the game looking for a much needed win, Baylor's Jo Lual-Acuil Jr. slams home the go-ahead dunk with 10 seconds left in double overtime to give the Bears a 74-73 victory.
videos.headline: Baylor edges Texas in 2OT thriller
